      "backgroundColor": "#fff3bf",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3",
      "roundness": { "type": 3 },
      "seed": 1040,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 2040,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776759578000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "txt-problems",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 786,
      "y": 996,
      "width": 568,
      "height": 188,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b4",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1041,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 2041,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776759578000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "QingShuClaw 解决的问题\n• 把平台治理好的 Tool / Skill 送到业务一线桌面\n• 把“后端能力”变成“用户可直接使用的工作助手”\n• 降低复杂 SQL、跨系统切换、口径不一致的成本\n• 让分析、执行、汇报在一次会话中闭环完成",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "box-strategy",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 1440,
      "y": 970,
      "width": 640,
      "height": 240,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffd8a8",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b5",
      "roundness": { "type": 3 },
      "seed": 1042,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 2042,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776759578000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false
    },
    {
      "id": "txt-strategy",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1464,
      "y": 990,
      "width": 592,
      "height": 194,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1043,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 2043,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776759578000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "企业级数据 AI 驱动战略闭环\n垂域数据 -> 统一语义模型 -> 可治理 Tool -> 可复用 Skill -> 可投放 Agent -> QingShuClaw 一线应用 -> 业务反馈回流\n\n结果：标准口径、权限可控、能力复用、快速落地；同时各数据域中与 Tool 绑定的 SQL 会持续沉淀为知识库，为 AI 自动生成 SQL、自动规划 Skill、自动生成 Tool 打下基础，把“数据资产”与“AI 能力资产”一起管理好。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
